The paper discusses techniques for improving search performance, specifically in web search, by combining multiple sources of information using rank fusion. This topic falls under the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) and data structures (cs.DS) to improve efficiency. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) for re-ranking approaches. Finally, the paper mentions the use of large-scale datasets (cs.DB) for experimental evaluation.
